"""TOF validator — P1.3 complete.

Read-only validator and pipeline consistency linter.
Dependencies: Python stdlib + PyYAML.

History: P0.1-P0.3 runtime hardening → P1.1-P1.3 execution layer → P2.x fidelity.
See IMPLEMENTATION_STATUS.md for full capability matrix.
"""

